# Page Tours

<img style="float:left; margin-right: 20px;" src="<%- @getUrl('/img/tour.png') %>">

Tours are located in the left sidebar.  They represent a grouping of
pages on your monitor site.

When a tour is selected from the sidebar, the first page of the tour is loaded and
a tour control is displayed at the bottom of the screen.  The tour runs until it is
stopped from the control.

Most tours are configured to automatically cycle through the pages at a specified interval.

