## Building Tours

<img style="float:right; margin-left: 40px; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 10px" src="<%- @getUrl('/img/tour_settings.png') %>">

While hovering over the Tours heading in the sidebar,
a Tour Settings option appears in the heading.

<img style="margin: 20px; border-radius: 8px;" src="<%- @getUrl('/img/tour_manage.png') %>">

Clicking that icon opens the Tour Settings panel (shown at the right) where you can add new tours,
manage tour pages, and remove tours.

Your changes are saved by pressing the Save button.


